Class CommandCore

java.lang.Object
com.iantapply.wynncraft.command.CommandCore
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor
public class CommandCore extends Object implements org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor
A class with utilities to manage the core functionality regarding commands registered and used on the Wynncraft server.
